title: Spell of Fate by Mayer Alan Brenner
description:
Book 3 in The Dance of Gods series.

Brenner returns to the world of Catastrophe's Spell and Spell of Intrigue, where trouble is brewing for mortals and gods alike. Maximillian the Vaguely Disreputable comes closer to solving the laws of conservation of magic and toppling the gods' power base while the Creeping Sword is drawn into the fighting between the gods.
